episodes.title: Muse
episodes.plot: Past and present collide in Oxford, as the auction of a priceless Faberge Egg gets underway at Lonsdale College.

episodes.title: Cartouche
episodes.plot: The unexplained poisoning of a former detective sergeant leads Endeavour and Thursday to a local cinema.

episodes.title: Passenger
episodes.plot: The railway takes center stage as Endeavour investigates the disappearance of a local woman - with initial fears linking it to the unsolved murder of a teenager, killed several years earlier.

episodes.title: Colours
episodes.plot: A photo-shoot on an army base turns sinister when one of the models is found dead. But the investigation is complicated when Sam Thursday is revealed to be involved.

episodes.title: Quartet
episodes.plot: An assassination attempt at an international sporting event opens a new case for Endeavour and Thursday, but their investigation is quickly brought to an unexpected end.

episodes.title: Icarus
episodes.plot: After the mysterious disappearance of a teacher, Endeavour finds himself investigating the dark and secret world of a public school.
